# 9.9 Best Practice

## Core Principles

- Coordinate early
- Be clear and concise
- Confirm critical information

---

## Golden Rules

- Do not transfer unresolved conflicts
- Do not assume acceptance
- Maintain agreed conditions

---

## Professional Standard

- Seamless transfers
- Predictable traffic flow
- Minimal coordination required

---

## Key Takeaway

> Good coordination is invisible — poor coordination is immediately obvious.
